					"type": 23,
					"value": "Players talk to the real Quenora at the blushing mermaid. In the top half of this dialogue, she's been saved from the hag by the players.\r\n\r\nIn the bottom half of the dialogue, the hag is never in BG. So this is just Quenora being her usual charming hungover as hell self."
